{"tid":1911177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垂範亞洲建共和　1928年香港人教中華民國　法治","createTime":"2020-03-05T07:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T07:09:45.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fedd4f7c2abe2b7ede825fd20ed75d66b89481b","tid":1911177,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663843483851726&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2663843483851726%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=bb764653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663843483851726&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n輿論談及【法治】，最早最早見於1928年《工商日報》創辦人洪興錦寫嘅文章。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4BJzGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4BJzGe.jpg&h=5042abcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663424780560263&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2663424780560263%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=63053640\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663424780560263&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n「法治精神」從來都係共產黨語嘅證據。<br />\n<br />\n1984賣豬仔之前，呢四隻字只出現過喺大公報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxGhD5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxGhD5H.jpg&h=d1cf7de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWan Leung Wong 法治係政府守法<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung 法治要共和才會的。日本人翻譯做共和，意思是分散力量的和平共存。單一力量只能自律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663400593896015&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2663400593896015%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=6b137441\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2663400593896015&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n原來「教育青少年法治精神」、「具備法治意識，自發地遵守法律」係楊鐵樑呢條壽頭發明嘅。唔怪得講極法治都仲係被扭曲定義啦，要undo 30年嘅損害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1hD7X7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1hD7X7.jpg&h=30142fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2664993347070073&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2664993347070073%26set%3Da.1403846723184748%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=6df3047a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2664993347070073&amp;set=a.1403846723184748&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n1947年上海軍隊「濫捕」，家長眾籌打官司，法庭拖延n個月，比人屌咁樣係違背法治。<br />\n<br />\n幾十年後，香港同樣情況degenerate到淨係識得「有險可守」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3bRaK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3bRaK9.jpg&h=1ac63c60&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}